title: Sound On: Brexit, U.K. Trade Deal In Congress
itunes:title: Sound On: Brexit, U.K. Trade Deal In Congress
description:
Alexandra Phillips, MEP for the Brexit Party representing South East England discusses the latest developments for a Brexit deal and House Speaker Nancy Pelosi’s recent comments opposing a U.S.-U.K. trade deal that would threaten the Good Friday Agreement.
